---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - CoreShot">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-[#0F172A] pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-red max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">CoreShot Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] mb-8">
          <strong>Effective Date: November 5, 2025</strong><br />
          <strong>Last Updated: November 5, 2025</strong>
        </p>

        <hr class="border-white/10 my-8" />

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. General Provisions</h2>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li>
              <strong>Service Provider</strong>: CoreShot Sp. z o.o., VAT: [INSERT VAT], Company No:
              [INSERT REGON].
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Services</strong>:
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
                <li>Sale of shooting accessories via the coreshot.eu online store.</li>
                <li>
                  Mobile/web application <strong>CoreShot Range Manager</strong> (shooting range management,
                  reservations, results).
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              Terms available at: <a href="/en/terms" class="text-[#E11D48] hover:underline"
                >coreshot.eu/terms</a
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Orders and Delivery</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-white/10 text-[#E5E7EB]">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-white/5">
                  <th class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-left">Stage</th>
                  <th class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-left">Details</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Ordering</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3"
                    >Cart → payment (Stripe/PayU) → email confirmation</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-white/5">
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Processing time</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3"
                    >1-3 business days (PL), 3-7 days (EU)</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Shipping costs</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">DHL/InPost – calculator in cart</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-white/5">
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Returns</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">14 days (EU law), undamaged goods</td
                  >
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. CoreShot Range Manager Account</h2>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li><strong>Registration</strong>: email + password (Supabase Auth).</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Requirements</strong>:
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
                <li>Age ≥ 18 years.</li>
                <li>Shooting license (optional – for premium features).</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Features</strong>:
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
                <li>Lane reservations.</li>
                <li>Score tracking (caliber, distance, accuracy).</li>
                <li>PDF/CSV export.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Account deletion</strong>: Settings → "Delete account" → data removed within
              30 days.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Payments and Subscriptions</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-white/10 text-[#E5E7EB]">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-white/5">
                  <th class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-left">Plan</th>
                  <th class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-left">Price</th>
                  <th class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-left">Features</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Free</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">0 €</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Basic results, 1 range</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-white/5">
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Pro</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">9.99 €/month</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3"
                    >Unlimited ranges, export, scope integration</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Enterprise</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Contact</td>
                  <td class="border border-white/10 px-4 py-3">Dedicated API, 24/7 support</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#E5E7EB] mt-4">
            <strong>Cancellation</strong>: anytime – no charges for next period.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Copyright and License</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li><strong>Application</strong>: Non-exclusive, non-transferable license.</li>
            <li>
              <strong>User content</strong> (results, photos): You grant CoreShot a non-exclusive license
              for anonymized analysis (industry statistics).
            </li>
            <li><strong>Prohibited</strong>: Reverse engineering, APK modification.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Liability</h2>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li>
              <strong>Exclusion</strong>: We are not liable for:
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
                <li>Errors in user-entered data.</li>
                <li>Injuries at shooting ranges.</li>
                <li>Force majeure.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Limit</strong>: Maximum liability = order value.</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Complaints</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li>
              <strong>Method</strong>: email <a href="#" class="text-[#E11D48] hover:underline"
                >support@coreshot.eu</a
              >
            </li>
            <li><strong>Deadline</strong>: 14 days from receipt of goods / notice of defect.</li>
            <li><strong>Response</strong>: 14 days.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Final Provisions</h2>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[#E5E7EB]">
            <li><strong>Applicable law</strong>: Polish law.</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Jurisdiction</strong>: Court competent for CoreShot's registered office.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Changes</strong>: Email notification 14 days in advance.</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <hr class="border-white/10 my-8" />

        <p class="text-center text-xl text-white font-semibold">
          <strong>CoreShot™ – Precision. Technology. Reliability.</strong>
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .prose ul,
  .prose ol {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
